<doc id="140804" wikidata="Q6708815" url="?curid=140804" title="Lynette Chico">
<text>Lynette Chico (born April 22, 1971) is a Puerto Rican fashion model, actress and radio host on 98.5 FM Cadena Salsoul Puerto Rican radio station. She has had parts in many of Puerto Rico&#x27;s television shows.

==Puerto Rican television==
* &quot;Estudio 69&quot; (she plays &quot;La Chacha&quot;, a French maid) with Miguel Morales
* &quot;Dame un Break&quot;
* &quot;No te Duermas&quot;
* &quot;El Super Show&quot;
* Channel 52 &quot;V Fifty Two&quot; (host of the local music show)

==Calendars==
She has modeled in many calendars, including &quot;2008 Puerto Rican Sensation&quot;.

==Film==
She is part of the cast in Daddy Yankee&#x27;s upcoming movie &quot;Talento de Barrio&quot;.

==Personal life==
Her sister, Leticia Rodriguez, is also an actress.

